Mobirix Co., Ltd. Privacy Policy
Mobirix Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as the “Company”) guides users through the procedures and standards for handling personal information in accordance with Article 30 of the 「Personal Information Protection Act」 so that users can safely use the homepage and mobile game service, and promptly resolves related grievances. We establish and disclose the following personal information processing policy in order to process it smoothly.
This privacy policy may change due to changes in related laws and guidelines or changes in the company's internal policies.
Article 1 [Items of personal information collected and used]
① For user identification, personal information may be collected as follows.
- [Required] Member information: external platform ID (Google, Apple, Facebook), domestic and foreign information
② When using game and portal services, comply with relevant laws, protect accounts and items, prevent fraudulent users, and provide stable service
The following information can be automatically collected and generated for provision, etc.
- [Required] When installing and using the game: nickname, download history, service use record, access log (including IP address), Bad use record, game version, payment record, terminal information (model name, OS information, terminal language and country information), device identification value, location information, Advertisement ID
③ When using the customer center to ensure smooth service use, additional information will be collected as follows.
- [Required] Customer consultation and complaint handling service: email address, game name, game ID, nickname, UID
- [Optional] Customer consultation and complaint handling service: Information required to confirm and respond to inquiries, terminal information (operating system, OS version, device ID, terminal model name), Payment details
④ Upon user request, personal information is requested as follows in order to process a refund. Depending on your payment information
The information collected may differ, and separate consent is obtained when necessary. Additionally, if the user is a minor
When processing a refund, additional information may be requested to verify your identity and the relationship with your legal representative.
- [Required] Payment/refund related information: email address, game name, game ID, nickname
- [Optional] Information related to payment/refund: Documents proving real name and family relationship to confirm payment in case of cancellation of payment by a minor (copy of resident registration / certificate of family relationship), materials required to confirm name of payment method (certificate of confirmation of subscription by minor, SKT - User agreement registration details / KT - Membership ledger certificate / LG - Subscription confirmation), Payment method confirmation document (Card payment statement / Card name confirmation), Payment method confirmation document (Card payment statement / Card name confirmation) Terminal information ( Operating system, OS version, device ID, terminal model name)
⑤ If the user wants to participate in the company's events and marketing, the user's personal information can be collected and used.
However, in this case, separate consent is obtained from the user.
- [Optional] Consent to receive advertising information: e-mail address, mobile phone number
