Article 10 [Measures to Ensure Safety of Personal Information]
① In processing the personal information of users, the company does not allow personal information to be lost, stolen, leaked, forged, altered or damaged.
To ensure safety, we take the following measures.
Administrative measures: Establishment and implementation of internal management plan, training of employees and personal information handlers
Technical measures: management of access rights such as personal information processing system, installation and renewal of company-wide PC and server security programs
Physical measures: computer room access control
